@host = http://localhost:8080
@adminUserId = adminUser1
@adminPassword = Adm1nPass!
@categoryId = 100
@categoryName = 공지사항
@updatedCategoryName = 새 공지사항

### 관리자 회원가입 (status를 ADMIN으로 지정)
# @name adminSignUp
POST {{host}}/users/sign-up
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{adminUserId}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}",
  "name": "관리자 계정",
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "phone": "010-1111-1111",
  "address": "서울시 관리자동",
  "nickName": "관리자",
  "status": "ADMIN"
}

### 관리자 로그인 (세션 쿠키 저장)
# @name adminLogin
POST {{host}}/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{adminUserId}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}

### 카테고리 등록
# @name registerCategory
POST {{host}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": {{categoryId}},
  "name": "{{categoryName}}"
}

### 카테고리 수정
# @name updateCategory
PUT {{host}}/categories/{{categoryId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "{{updatedCategoryName}}"
}

### 카테고리 삭제
# @name deleteCategory
DELETE {{host}}/categories/{{categoryId}}

### 관리자 로그아웃 (선택)
# @name adminLogout
POST {{host}}/users/logout

